{"tid":1519567,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"到底中學生罷課應該點做？","createTime":"2019-08-30T15:12:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T16:07:11.000Z","uid":4637,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"73ad22cb06ae205b4b5e2aa834422241606726ef","tid":1519567,"uid":4637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:12:20.000Z","msg":"打嗰位師兄應該係中佬嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家體諒下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學生在校內罷課，作用甚微，<br />\n只影響到校內的運作;<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果穿著校服、在返學時間而齊齊走出學校，</span><br />\n效果就大大不同了！<br />\n<br />\n校服是中小學生的鐵布衫！<br />\n只要和平有序不暴力沒粗口，<br />\n沒人敢動中學生一條毛！<br />\n鄉黑不敢下手，<br />\n暴警無用武之地，<br />\n老解也不敢盲衝。<br />\n<br />\n這是「毒蛾正虎」死穴之一！<br />\n只要中學和平罷課、有序走出校園，<br />\n堅持一週以上，「不撤就罷」，<br />\n肯定响應更大、民意更強，<br />\n在真正「不受傷、不被捕」的情況下，<br />\n赢面甚大！<br />\n<br />\n唯一要鼓起勇氣，<br />\n同校內一定存在的「藍師」抗衡，<br />\n同可能已「染紅」的校長據理力爭。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">放心:<br />\n記過可以不理，開除於法不合;<br />\n校內肯定沒人會用肉身來攔阻你。</span>"},{"pid":"538aae985295c6281816275c18598c50f6704167","tid":1519567,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:14:14.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0qGgm0NOSfkDZSs230CVm%2Fs%3D&h=fd1bb84f\" data-auto-link ta